  D_384191091_D_384191091_D_412790539 AS A,

Query 2:

SELECT
  LEFT(CAST(Connect_ID AS String), 3) AS ID,
  D_384191091.D_384191091 AS Race,
  D_384191091.D_747350323 AS Other
  FROM
  `nih-nci-dceg-connect-stg-5519.Connect.module1_v1`
WHERE Connect_ID IN (1541654186, 6173331456,3455671424,2198619957,1920159439);
